ural areas or shifts in market prices can push poor families over the brink the families reap assists are those on the edge attempting to improve their future livelihood with long term investments including education while struggling to make ends meet on a daily basis here are a sampling of stories from rural china to help depict the daily life our clients lead ban baohong ke xianpeng liu zhenlong meng xiangjun han jing stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
